Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador

Enum UnitSimulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UnitSimulator>
      • org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.UnitSimulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<UnitSimulator>, EventProcessor
    public enum UnitSimulator
extends Enum<UnitSimulator>
implements EventProcessor
    The UnitSimulator is a singleton responsible for registering/removing AbstractSimulationUnits to/from the simulation, enabling the units' sensors and loading the units' applications. Note: The UnitSimulator is only concerned about units equipped with applications.
